Tolong, tinggalkan aku sendiri.
- Malishka...

00:09:40.560 --> 00:09:41.800
Silakan!

00:09:41.960 --> 00:09:45.240
Saya mohon padamu.  Keluar saja
dari kamarku, kalian berdua.  Silakan!

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:46.960
Bibi...
- Pergi.  Bawa dia bersama.

00:09:47.800 --> 00:09:49.040
'Tetap dalam batas Anda!'

00:09:50.320 --> 00:09:51.320
Omong kosong.

00:09:53.280 --> 00:09:54.360
Tidak, Nelam.

